{"tid":379644,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[耳機撚]討論下香港各大耳機電(30)","createTime":"2017-08-29T13:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T13:32:13.000Z","uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b904a8b0214252141c1eb40092ffa61f0d220b9a","tid":379644,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"各位新黎既巴絲請詳細閱讀第一頁，以免問題不停回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新黎既巴/絲打歡迎留一留低自己聽歌器材既資料(新link)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheet%2Fviewform%3Fformkey%3DdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b84e8f6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢頁可以睇番其他巴打填左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheet%2Fccc%3Fkey%3D0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ccda5866\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/eargay2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Feargay2&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4e856d07\" target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/eargay2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耳機潮文合集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k%2Fedit&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4661b015\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耳機推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8%2Fedit&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bc1ce3be\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCM推介(有待修改)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ierm更已新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM%2Fedit&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4a2c0394\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAmp推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc%2Fedit&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9680ea15\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDIY AMP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M%2Fedit&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d4b0962b\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFAQ：<br />\n<br />\nQ1：1000蚊之內budget買咩入耳式好？<br />\n<br />\nA1：出旺角各大耳機鋪試下(唔試過點知邊隻最適合自己？)<br />\n<br />\n毒撚到冇朋友巴打真心推介：hifiman re400，平衡度相當高，極之適合雜食。<br />\n<br />\n重Bass：se215(LE)、sony xb90ex (停左產難搵)<br />\n<br />\n人聲/平衡：mc5(難推)、fxd80(停左產難搵)、philips s2、heaven ii、ath-im50、ath-im70、sony xba-100、a1、jvc fxt208se，仲有對冇得試既apple earpod。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ2：耳機得番一邊有聲點搞？<br />\n<br />\nA2：依個情況多數係條耳機線暗斷，仲有保養就拎上代理換。<br />\n<br />\n過左保可以上恆源/波sir(大伏，手功麻麻)/Hercules小修小寶工作室(服務同手功較好)道整或者自已剪左個插頭焊過個新既。<br />\n<br />\n但未必一定成功(亦有可能中伏)，<br />\n<br />\n亦可以考慮買過對新既耳機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ3：耳棉或耳膠爛左去邊道買番黎換？<br />\n<br />\nA3：基本上各大耳機店都有Comply棉賣(好易爛)，<br />\n<br />\n推介monster super tips，隔音唔錯之餘仲幾耐用。<br />\n<br />\n另外耳棉耳膠係旺角德發地庫都有得賣(三節膠最隔音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，<br />\n<br />\n大約$40-$50一對。"},{"pid":"d02c256288b3a6448e33233bdccc5a30e0f90c47","tid":379644,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">亦軒耳機音樂世界</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingo-hmw.com/home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingo-hmw.com%2Fhome%2F&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=db6a9a3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingo-hmw.com/home/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多好多好多耳機免費任試，面皮夠厚既話，可試足一個下午<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品種類繁多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分店多，地點便利<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦軒論壇個二手買賣區，間中會搵到筍野(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你一定要知價，否則做水魚)<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品價錢偏貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大部份貨品都賣貴過甚他鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左鋪後，佢個論壇變了質，好多野都俾人大吹一餐，或人云亦云，D意見睇下就算，最緊要親自試聽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人流多，唔少耳機都俾人試到殘晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">金聲耳筒專門店</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.headphonehk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.headphonehk.com%2F&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1ae8a01b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.headphonehk.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔少耳機都可以任試 (但冇亦軒咁多)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總店人流較少，環境靜D，可以專心D試耳機，耳機也比較新淨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分店多，地點尚算方便<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢比亦軒平<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買野前切記一定要問清楚是行定水貨、保養條款、檢查行貨包裝上有沒有香港代理的貼紙和標籤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">AV2000</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.av2000.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.av2000.com.hk&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3389019f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.av2000.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢[rgb(255, 192, 203)]<del>通常比其他鋪頭</del>[/rgb(255, 192, 203)]平，會講明係行貨定水貨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 據聞個老闆以前在某影音鋪打工，對影音產品既意見較專業<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野都冇得試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鋪頭細小，貨品款式不及亦軒、金聲咁多，更沒有售賣大陸牌子耳機，以大牌子的熱門貨品為主<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">DMA 泛音</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dma-audio.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dma-audio.com%2F&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bc8db34d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dma-audio.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多高檔野試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D牌子都做返街價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有出自己牌子既HP架，都有ATH架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有SOUND CARD，DAC，AMP，喇叭，DAP賣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子相對比較齊<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某D牌子仍屬於貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢賣既多數都係高檔貨，小朋友玩唔起，得個睇字 (依家其實都有唔少入門野賣)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del>冇DENON</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0984aef1272fe331c4b8965e994e90c444dd375","tid":379644,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Jaben HK</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jaben.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jaben.com.hk%2F&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9055c7dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jaben.com.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多貴野試，做cm可以即場做埋耳印<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多間入面試耳機最好環境，閒日時間少人夠晒靜，任試唔嬲<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比較貴，視姦play<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恆源</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fs-digital.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs-digital.net%2F&d=FfZiCF3AVsKEUqZWuhr%2F0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=06476f42\" target=\"_blank\">http://fs-digital.net/</a><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有自家品牌，地方比較靜<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D產品都係戇鳩調音，乜都賣得貴過人，馬撚又小器又封閉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>天下影音：(16/F)</strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D貨會劈價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係比較有名氣牌子 (唔會有大陸牌子)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣HI-FI種類多，有興趣巴打可以順便望望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行內消息：由Denon代理開既 (好難証實，但有Denon野賣，DMA係冇Denon野)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有分店，但System及貨量都係獨立，所以佢既分店呢間冇可以走去第間睇睇或者格價<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試既多數係HP<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有平野賣，但唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要格價(拿，唔好話我唔提)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 限定版唔洗諗，應該好難會入到手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行內消息：T字頭代理會唔派貨，正如AX2XXX咁 (原因都係個價做壞市)，換句話講唔一定有HIT既貨品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似冇MONSTER貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>華仁：(10/F)</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢都肯追貼街價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環境好 (但唔太靜，如果有人試HI-FI)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有HI-FI野睇同小量DAC/AMP野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有BD賣 (價錢唔好諗佢平)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店員幾NICE (第一次上去果時，第二次就差D笑容，但佢都樂意拎俾你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旗艦級IEM都有得試，etc. IE8、SE535<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子小 只有ATH SEN記 加MONSTER同SHURE<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢唔好最平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主打HI-FI 所以唔好望D野好齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 容納人數小，試聽頂多4、5人已經叫FULL<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英京：(8/F</span>)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同天下(16/F)差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺AMP/DAC種類較多(對比16/F)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試耳機服務好過(16/F)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可訂貨<br />\n<br />\nBAD <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同天下(16/F)差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地唔太SURE停產與否，都會叫你訂貨，例如W1000 (某D對呢方面唔太熟既職員會咁做)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國際影音：(7/F</span>)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒男O岩，望價睇野，佢都唔點理你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢都同友誠上下撞<br />\n<br />\nBAD <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子小<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太多耳機選擇"}]}